http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Maryland State Curriculum - Personal Financial Literacy Education

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The State Curriculum for Personal Financial Literacy Education provides standards, indicators, and objectives for use in creating local curricula – thus defining what students should know and be able to do. Local leaders will choose the approach to implementation and determine how best to provide students with instruction across the learning levels.
